What is AI Agent ?
An AI agent is an autonomous software system designed to perceive its environment, reason, and act to achieve specific goals with minimal human intervention.

Key characteristics :

| Characteristic       | Explanation               |
| -------------------- | ------------------------- |
| **Autonomy**         | Works on its own          |
| **Reactivity**       | Responds to environment   |
| **Proactiveness**    | Takes initiative          |
| **Reasoning**        | Breaks tasks into steps   |
| **Tool Use**         | Uses APIs, search, email  |
| **Memory**           | Remembers context         |
| **Learning**         | Improves behavior         |
| **Natural Language** | Communicates with humans  |
| **Acting**           | Performs real actions     |
| **Goal Completion**  | Finishes tasks end-to-end |

Architecture 

                      ┌────────────────────────┐
                      │        User Input       │
                      └────────────┬────────────┘
                                   │
                                   ▼
                     ┌──────────────────────────┐
                     │  Natural Language Layer   │
                     │ (Instruction + Parsing)   │
                     └────────────┬──────────────┘
                                   │
                                   ▼
                   ┌──────────────────────────────┐
                   │     Reasoning & Planning      │
                   │ (ReAct / Chain-of-Thought /   │
                   │   Planner / Decision Maker)   │
                   └────────────┬──────────────────┘
                                │
                      ┌─────────┴─────────┐
                      ▼                   ▼
        ┌──────────────────────┐   ┌──────────────────────┐
        │  Tool Selector        │   │ Memory Manager       │
        │ (Which tool to use?) │   │ (Short/Long-term     │
        └──────────┬───────────┘   │  memory retrieval)   │
                   │               └─────────┬────────────┘
                   ▼                         │
         ┌──────────────────────┐            │
         │  Tool / Function     │◄───────────┘
         │   Execution Layer    │
         │ (Search, API calls,  │
         │  DB, Email, Python)  │
         └──────────┬───────────┘
                    │
                    ▼
       ┌────────────────────────────┐
       │   Observation Processing   │
       │ (Read tool results & feed │
       │  back into reasoning)     │
       └──────────┬───────────────┘
                  │
                  ▼
       ┌────────────────────────────┐
       │   Response Generation       │
       │ (Final answer to user)      │
       └──────────┬───────────────┘
                  │
                  ▼
            ┌───────────────┐
            │  User Output   │
            └───────────────┘

